Class AdminController

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.controllers.AdminController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class AdminController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    FXML Controller class for admin.fxml

    This class handles the interaction from the user in the Administration scene. The administration scene is the opening scene when you open the application. It has the Add New Athlete, Search Athletes, Questionaire Editor, and Printable Forms buttons.
